@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_hatyzx(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.sin((wp.exp(v1 + 0.97) - wp.cos(tmp + 0.39)))
    v0 = tmp
    tmp = 0.62
    v0 = (0.31 - wp.exp((v1 + 0.40 / v2 + 0.84)))
    v1 = (v2 - wp.cos((v1 + 0.81 - v2 + 0.99)))
    v1 = v1
    tmp = (wp.sin((v1 + 0.41 / v1 + 0.71)) - ((v2 + 0.28 * tmp + 0.43) * v0))
    v0 = 0.71
    data[tid] = v0
